lirc daemon setting for Human Interface Device on  Arch linux
=============================================================
Howto install these scripts:

lircd               ==>       /etc/rc.d/lircd

lircd.conf          ==>       /etc/lircd.conf

lirc/lircd.conf     ==>       /etc/lirc/lircd.conf

LIL.map             ==>       map file for Moovida media center , if you use HID (en.wikipedia.org/wiki/HID) device
